Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.09,0:00:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... that Takita...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she fell off the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... if we had been more careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.55,0:00:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no one's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... to think this is the\Nlast image we'd have of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I was throwing my pants\Nand whatnot at her every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Takita!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All things considered,\Nshe was a good girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In three or so years she'd have\Nshined as a draker...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh!! Come on, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.62,0:00:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being so ominous, would you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys... even if they're wounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,dragons not always fall head first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So if she was clinging on to it\Nuntil the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe... she's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say whatever you want, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We barely can't even see anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we even going to search for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:01:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Yoshi-san, make me\Nsome salo sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.73,0:01:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, very sweet tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-Eh?\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be on guard without sleeping tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Her being turned to mincemeat, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We... didn't manage to catch\Nthat dragon, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta thank this little guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been protecting you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It might think you're its mother\Nor something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that injury on your leg\Ngot infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't happen to pass by\Nthis deep chasm,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd have died in the gutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what happened to the dissection?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I took out the entrails and have it\Nsubmerged over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure have luck on your side, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Luck's always been about the only\Nthing I had going for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I always make it with deer or boar,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but with dragon it's the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"Salted cabbage and dragon brain hunter stew\Nwith roasted bone marrow"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you don't mind I used\Nsome of your dragon's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a stew made by matagi hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, what a nice smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my favourite dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How does a dragon's brain taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty weakened, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't eat while you have some\Nstrength left, you won't be able to\Nstomach anything later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because it's this little one's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sticky but smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What an intense flavour!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! I can feel the nourishment\Npermeating in every single of my organs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you doing it on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... it's so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's super delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta thank its mother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to eat the preys you hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the more you eat\Nthe better you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone similar to you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a man, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, a camp in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the matagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,hunt with this area as a base\Nduring this season.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? My, how rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have a guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and a little one as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet everyone is worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Or they think I'm already dead
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and left already...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The ointment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm definitely gonna bring you\Nback to your pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:08:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to be in perfect health first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... it's quite swollen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I did all I could, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Huh? Ascella-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, bite this leaf and endure it\Nfor a bit, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny is an expert with the needle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, look at this landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... kind of amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It lets out some smoke every few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mount Kin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said that when that mountain\Nlets out smoke, dragons will pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the smoke call the dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows, it's just a superstition\Nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishes swim in the sea,\Nbeasts walk on the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,dragons fly in the sky,\Nand people live on the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the legend,\Nour ancestors
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,arrived to this valley chasing dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Chased out of their lands,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,our ancestors, who were travelling\Nsearching for a new world,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,saw a dragon fall from the sky\Nand followed its trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And they arrived to this valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They thought it was some kind of good omen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and decided to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, and that's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-Rest for a while, okay?\N-Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks kinda down, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hungry too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wheat porridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoghurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bean paste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing works.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems it doesn't like any of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a creature from the sky,\Nso maybe it eats things from the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Things from the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Some time ago, a small dragon\Nhappened to get into the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was drawn in by the smell\Nof dragon oil...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Insert the blade between the red meat\Nand the fat and cut it away along with the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When you've cut it in pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave a bit of skin and add\Nsome thin cuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks... kind of like a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, this is called\N"making into a book".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,While it boils, scoop out\Nthe oil that floats
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and after it's extracted,\Nadd the oil cake as fuel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, some people eat it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's dragon oil done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You got quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use it both for cooking\Nand as lamp oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh, nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's dragon oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, do it... okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't bear looking at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we add an egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, an egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:12:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When she was feeling down,\NI used to make it for her like this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha- that was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, pour the oil slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Little by little, like a thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is to continue mixing it\Nwhile you add the oil, she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's thickening!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mayonnaise with dragon oil and whole egg"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It ate it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's eating, it's eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold the little thing and give it to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like a real mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what are Mika-san\Nand the others doing right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What... are they eating...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm... what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The little one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... it's all wrinkly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It ate properly and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fish in the sea...\Nbeasts in the mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This one... probably can't live on land.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountain is letting out\Na lot of smoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When the smoke blows,\Ndragons will pass by...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:13:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ascella-san, I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... you're going\Nto the mountain now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't with that leg!\NIt's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,At least wait till the sun goes up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wait, it'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It has never seen other dragons like\Nitself nor flown in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If I abandon it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I... have the feeling I won't be able\Nto go back to being a draker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm the one who saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna let that go to waste\NI won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna prepare, so wait a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,See, what did I tell you?\NWant me to go slower?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll manage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That mountain is very steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even matagi hunters don't go\Nthere often... damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, if I ain't kind to a fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, want to rest for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine... this pain isn't even\Nthe worst I've had...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you didn't mistake it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It quickly hid behind the clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was definitely that dragon pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"Should", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, it gets way too dangerous\Nafter this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you done enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As high as I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As closer as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But, girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what makes you go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the same as you, Ascella-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lump me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so honest you need to add\N"stupidly" before it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the point where Takita fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,During the search, we detected\Nthe dragon pod again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We started pursuing it and\Nlost sight of it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Gaga said,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that pod is on their way to\Na certain place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That "ferry" definitely has a destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with that, but
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking that this final destination
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is where Takita-san will be
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't a bit too optimistic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's the possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that the dragon that fell with her\Ncontinued flying chasing the pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any other clue anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:16:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If we know their destination,\Nwe can also follow the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We can narrow down the search scope\Nquite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... we have half a day left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go with this, it's our only bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You have barely slept, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The horizon is lighting up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to your room and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in front of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprisingly talkative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Find her, and discover it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:18:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... even if we call it destination,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.96,0:18:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,who knows where on earth are\Nthe dragons heading to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And with this field of vision,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,if we don't narrow down\Nthe area even more, we can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.06,0:18:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems there's a legend about dragons\Nin the stories of the matagi of this area...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, this is probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about the "ferry",\Nor so I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that trustworthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should believe in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find Takita, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, don't look down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,For the love of...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's bad for my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The pod... is changing its shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it going somewhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You see it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ride the wind and go back to the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry up,\Nthey'll leave you behind, go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come back, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a dragon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Quin... Zaza...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
